name: jam cat
description: Jam Cat: The Sticky Situation of Crypto In a world where digital currencies roamed free, there was a legend whispered among the memes: the tale of Jam Cat, the sticky crypto feline. One fateful day, an ordinary house cat, while licking a jar of jam, accidentally stumbled upon a laptop left open to a crypto exchange. With a paw slick with jam, our hero clicked on "Create New Coin" and thus, Jam Cat was born - a cryptocurrency as sweet as the jam that birthed it.
